      "summary": "El Ezaby - Egypt‚Äôs #1 pharmacy network - partnered with Stackhubs to modernize connectivity across 450+ branches in all governorates. We designed and delivered a nationwide SD-WAN (VMware VeloCloud) with high availability at the Data Center and HQ, then rolled out one edge per branch with tiered Internet redundancy (Platinum/Gold/Silver). The entire deployment was completed in 3 months, and Stackhubs now operates the platform as a 3-year managed service, ensuring performance, security, and 24/7 support.",
